@startuml
title Athlete View Schedule
actor Athlete
participant "Web App" as WA
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "App Server" as AS
database "Database" as DB

Athlete -> WA: View schedule
WA -> API: Send schedule data request
API -> AS: Process schedule data request
AS -> DB: Query schedule data for specific athlete
AS --> API: Return schedule data
API --> WA: Return schedule data
WA --> Athlete: Display schedule
@enduml